{"id": "ChIJy4FbaQB_hYARpqpLj7W7X_o", "rating": 4.6, "userRatingCount": 185, "displayName": {"text": "Butterfish Sushi", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJy4FbaQB_hYARpqpLj7W7X_o/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twdVJYQmFhSE5TUTFoR1owZFRjM2hxVnpac1JVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Quite simply some of the best sushi you will find in the Bay. When normally good Japanese restaurants break the bank, the quality for the price here is unmatched. With only a handful of seats within, make sure to call ahead to guarantee a spot. Also a perfect date-night spot, 10/10 would recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Quite simply some of the best sushi you will find in the Bay. When normally good Japanese restaurants break the bank, the quality for the price here is unmatched. With only a handful of seats within, make sure to call ahead to guarantee a spot. Also a perfect date-night spot, 10/10 would recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alex", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109369639505458183196/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0IIohX-cVYKp-uzgDA5vNaRoPUUvH0DglAdgFFX6KNMehdWM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-02T04:27:55.011129271Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twdVJYQmFhSE5TUTFoR1owZFRjM2hxVnpac1JVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twdVJYQmFhSE5TUTFoR1owZFRjM2hxVnpac1JVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f00695b81cb:0xfa5fbbb58f4baaa6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJy4FbaQB_hYARpqpLj7W7X_o/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kMlMwRlFlWEV3TjBWZk1qWTVhMUpXYW01aVoyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This place is incredible in food, service, and atmosphere. Such amazing quality fish and delicious dishes.\n\nMy favorite was their hand rolls and the hirame usuzukuri (like a carpaccio). Even their green tea was made well, not bitter at all - so smooth. I dont think you could get anything wrong here.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place is incredible in food, service, and atmosphere. Such amazing quality fish and delicious dishes.\n\nMy favorite was their hand rolls and the hirame usuzukuri (like a carpaccio). Even their green tea was made well, not bitter at all - so smooth. I dont think you could get anything wrong here.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Rab", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110390819025211899529/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIxPTxYNieD8uCfoTznrw57Ju_5oF9HXbqf82hzhwti265uXw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-01T17:44:23.558089441Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kMlMwRlFlWEV3TjBWZk1qWTVhMUpXYW01aVoyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kMlMwRlFlWEV3TjBWZk1qWTVhMUpXYW01aVoyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f00695b81cb:0xfa5fbbb58f4baaa6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJy4FbaQB_hYARpqpLj7W7X_o/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GNlRsWk1WMEZrY2tSbGNEbEhkMWQyZVZwaVpFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Ok so I have pretty much given up eating sushi cause the quality even at highly rated places seems to be a bit meh now a days. Stumbled on Butterfish last night and I was literally transported back to Japan!\nI wish I could give them 10 stars. The food is just exquisite. Just come and try it yourself cause I really won't do justice to it with mere words.\nAnd the best part is you will receive the most hospitalable service which again transports you back to Japan. I wish other restaurants that are allegedly fancy would learn from this service team.\nWe enjoyed the food so much we over ate and it was totally worth the constitutional we needed to take after the meal😅\nThe fish is fresh, presented in innovative ways, they don't skimp on quantity, service completely above and beyond and lovely atmosphere.\nI give this place 10 happy bellies 😋😍", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Ok so I have pretty much given up eating sushi cause the quality even at highly rated places seems to be a bit meh now a days. Stumbled on Butterfish last night and I was literally transported back to Japan!\nI wish I could give them 10 stars. The food is just exquisite. Just come and try it yourself cause I really won't do justice to it with mere words.\nAnd the best part is you will receive the most hospitalable service which again transports you back to Japan. I wish other restaurants that are allegedly fancy would learn from this service team.\nWe enjoyed the food so much we over ate and it was totally worth the constitutional we needed to take after the meal😅\nThe fish is fresh, presented in innovative ways, they don't skimp on quantity, service completely above and beyond and lovely atmosphere.\nI give this place 10 happy bellies 😋😍", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tanya Sing", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110865917836509623305/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBq1eqeWIa8dkFNBJqQ8qlPqx7KzdeSup2wAUCwmx71HnfQj56=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-10T17:10:54.853344816Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GNlRsWk1WMEZrY2tSbGNEbEhkMWQyZVZwaVpFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GNlRsWk1WMEZrY2tSbGNEbEhkMWQyZVZwaVpFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f00695b81cb:0xfa5fbbb58f4baaa6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJy4FbaQB_hYARpqpLj7W7X_o/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0M1ZGVlRZbGhNWWpsSmNYSlNRMmhXYVZOdlduYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Came here last-minute looking for a good sushi place, and it was amazing. Atmosphere was indeed omakase-esque as other reviews state, really small and intimate. Sat at the bar and watched the chef at work, which I would highly recommend. I don't think you would go wrong at all ordering anything off the menu, everything we had was delicious. Portions on the salmon avocado roll were large, and there was never any padding for space in a roll with extra rice... just more fish. A bit on the pricey side, but very much worth it and really close to the best sushi I've had.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Came here last-minute looking for a good sushi place, and it was amazing. Atmosphere was indeed omakase-esque as other reviews state, really small and intimate. Sat at the bar and watched the chef at work, which I would highly recommend. I don't think you would go wrong at all ordering anything off the menu, everything we had was delicious. Portions on the salmon avocado roll were large, and there was never any padding for space in a roll with extra rice... just more fish. A bit on the pricey side, but very much worth it and really close to the best sushi I've had.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Henry Martin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115462540301778687908/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZlnpRqFfqXf5Hu_45t6dPGkwKGlUwu-EJLGZXRm5uV9e5p6o=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-21T01:21:02.369163120Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0M1ZGVlRZbGhNWWpsSmNYSlNRMmhXYVZOdlduYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0M1ZGVlRZbGhNWWpsSmNYSlNRMmhXYVZOdlduYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f00695b81cb:0xfa5fbbb58f4baaa6"}, {